00:31:30,130 --> 00:31:31,790
lie in stress and depression,

575
00:31:32,070 --> 00:31:33,600
not in the exercise itself.

576
00:31:34,830 --> 00:31:35,630
Qi Tian,

577
00:31:37,650 --> 00:31:40,180
you've targeted the wrong object of dislike.

578
00:31:44,430 --> 00:31:45,710
Studies show

579
00:31:45,790 --> 00:31:47,320
that stress and depression

580
00:31:48,090 --> 00:31:49,200
can lead to various illnesses,

581
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:51,890
such as ulcers, high blood pressure,

582
00:31:52,830 --> 00:31:55,150
irregular heartbeat, headaches,

583
00:31:55,790 --> 00:31:56,960
and more.

584
00:31:57,230 --> 00:31:59,990
The majority of human stress and depression

585
00:32:00,230 --> 00:32:01,470
stem from emotions

586
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:04,670
such as resentment, regret,

587
00:32:05,400 --> 00:32:07,260
anxiety, disappointment,

588
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:10,480
expectations, fear, sadness,

589
00:32:11,150 --> 00:32:12,750
and various other feelings.

590
00:32:14,310 --> 00:32:15,480
Removing them

591
00:32:16,120 --> 00:32:17,450
is indeed challenging.

592
00:32:18,910 --> 00:32:19,790
Therefore,

593
00:32:21,150 --> 00:32:22,640
you must learn

594
00:32:24,030 --> 00:32:26,680
how to calmly deal with them.

595
00:32:32,990 --> 00:32:33,810
Of course,

596
00:32:38,190 --> 00:32:41,320
for a nineteen-year-old like you,

597
00:32:41,560 --> 00:32:43,020
this is indeed difficult.

598
00:32:43,130 --> 00:32:45,460
Even for someone like me in their fifties,

599
00:32:46,110 --> 00:32:49,440
it's impossible to remain undisturbed in every situation.

600
00:32:53,590 --> 00:32:56,250
But this is a mandatory lesson for every athlete

601
00:32:58,030 --> 00:32:59,310
until retirement.

602
00:33:01,830 --> 00:33:02,570
So,

603
00:33:03,270 --> 00:33:04,190
Qi Tian,

604
00:33:05,190 --> 00:33:06,830
in the upcoming period,

605
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,440
your goal

606
00:33:08,870 --> 00:33:10,230
is to learn

607
00:33:10,320 --> 00:33:13,050
how to peacefully coexist with the distractions

608
00:33:13,110 --> 00:33:14,630
in your mind,

609
00:33:16,110 --> 00:33:18,670
and truly enter

610
00:33:18,870 --> 00:33:20,470
your own peak state.

611
00:33:33,000 --> 00:33:33,840
Qi Tian,

612
00:33:35,510 --> 00:33:36,710
keep up the good work.

613
00:33:37,190 --> 00:33:39,230
Why am I saying these words to you?

614
00:33:39,710 --> 00:33:42,230
Because in you, I see potential,

615
00:33:42,790 --> 00:33:45,710
the potential to reach greater heights.

616
00:33:49,520 --> 00:33:50,520
Don't ever

617
00:33:52,630 --> 00:33:53,990
give up.
